01:48.957 --> 01:51.752
I've been born-again my whole life.

01:52.669 --> 01:56.673
Accepting Jesus into your heart
and getting saved is a big decision...

01:57.424 --> 01:59.384
especially for a three-year-old.

02:02.054 --> 02:06.100
My faith taught me that everything
was a part of God's plan.

02:07.059 --> 02:10.645
Mom said that he even had a reason
for taking my father to heaven.

02:11.605 --> 02:15.092
She explained
that Daddy was with the angels.

02:15.192 --> 02:18.654
Well, I wanted to be with the angels, too.

02:21.198 --> 02:23.617
But God had other plans.

02:25.035 --> 02:27.855
Jesus became the center of my life.

02:27.955 --> 02:30.065
I still don't think
he's supposed to be white.

02:30.165 --> 02:33.569
- I was watching this thing on television...
- Of course, he's white.

02:33.669 --> 02:36.405
Gosh. Sometimes I think
my brother's retarded, too.

02:36.505 --> 02:39.199
No, your brother's not retarded.

02:39.299 --> 02:43.412
I was a member in good standing
of the Christian Jewels.

02:43.512 --> 02:45.748
It's sort of like a girl gang for Jesus.

02:45.848 --> 02:47.850
Don't kill your baby!

02:52.229 --> 02:53.255
Lillian Cummings.

02:53.355 --> 02:55.257
My mom was finally named the number one

02:55.357 --> 02:58.969
Christian interior decorator
for the entire region.

02:59.069 --> 03:03.390
And in spite of living
in what the Bible calls "the end times,"

03:03.490 --> 03:05.768
my future was looking bright.

03:05.868 --> 03:08.454
I had the perfect Christian boyfriend.

03:09.371 --> 03:14.126
And I was about to be a senior
at a really good Christian school.

03:37.149 --> 03:39.635
Two weeks before summer vacation ended,

03:39.735 --> 03:41.403
everything changed.

03:44.281 --> 03:46.058
My boyfriend and I played this game

03:46.158 --> 03:48.660
of telling each other secrets underwater.

03:49.411 --> 03:52.022
It's lame, I know.

03:52.122 --> 03:54.692
But this wasn't exactly
the MTV Beach House.

03:54.792 --> 03:57.945
Okay, now my turn.

03:58.045 --> 04:00.130
Okay, ready?

04:29.159 --> 04:30.160
Mary!

04:31.495 --> 04:33.689
Maybe it was because I was drowning,

04:33.789 --> 04:36.458
or the shock of Dean's confession...

04:37.167 --> 04:40.546
but at that moment, I had a vision.

04:47.261 --> 04:48.954
Dean needs you now.

04:49.054 --> 04:51.598
You must do all you can to help him.

04:58.564 --> 05:00.883
It's just a little bump, Mom.
I'm totally fine.

05:00.983 --> 05:02.818
Okay, all right.

05:03.444 --> 05:06.221
Mom was away at the Christian
Community Leader's Convention

05:06.321 --> 05:10.492
in Orlando with Pastor Skip...
the principal of my school.

05:11.201 --> 05:13.479
- Honey?
- Mom.

05:13.579 --> 05:16.231
You didn't tell me
Pastor Skip was so nice.

05:16.331 --> 05:18.359
Yeah, everybody loves him.

05:18.459 --> 05:21.945
We've been talking about setting up
our own fellowship programs

05:22.045 --> 05:23.964
when I get back to Cherry Hill.

05:25.007 --> 05:27.284
- I have to go.
- Come and get it.

05:27.384 --> 05:28.886
Come and get it.

05:30.220 --> 05:31.330
Love you.

05:31.430 --> 05:33.015
- I love you, too.
- Bye.

05:34.850 --> 05:36.435
What's shaking, Skip?

05:49.531 --> 05:52.059
How could my boyfriend be gay?

05:52.159 --> 05:54.687
He's, like, the best Christian I know.

05:54.787 --> 05:58.107
He's an athlete who's
constantly strengthening himself...

05:58.207 --> 06:01.293
physically, creatively,
and spiritually for the Lord.

06:04.088 --> 06:05.547
Thank you, Jesus.

06:07.341 --> 06:12.554
Why had he been stricken
with such a spiritually toxic affliction?

06:16.016 --> 06:20.129
I figured I needed to take
the most direct approach to saving him.

06:20.229 --> 06:22.523
I mean, it was Christ's will and all.

06:23.399 --> 06:26.093
Jesus spoke to you? In person?

06:26.193 --> 06:27.694
He trusts me.

06:28.737 --> 06:31.407
Okay? You're just gonna
have to trust me, too.

06:35.786 --> 06:38.122
- Just kiss me, okay?
- Okay.

06:39.665 --> 06:41.859
Dean and I worked diligently
on his problem

06:41.959 --> 06:43.819
for the rest of the summer.

06:43.919 --> 06:45.546
Anything yet?

06:50.801 --> 06:51.885
Now?

06:55.389 --> 06:57.015
Are you sure this isn't a sin?

06:58.016 --> 07:00.919
I was pretty sure
what we were doing wasn't a sin,

07:01.019 --> 07:04.048
but not sure enough
to give Dean what he really needed.

07:04.148 --> 07:08.694
I needed spiritual guidance
or a sign or something, and quick.

07:13.490 --> 07:17.853
Hilary Faye seemed to have
a spiritual solution for every problem.

07:17.953 --> 07:20.564
Christian girls have got to know
how to protect themselves.

07:20.664 --> 07:25.277
I mean, sure, Jesus could restore
my physical and spiritual virginity,

07:25.377 --> 07:29.198
especially if I lost it
to some rapist, but...

07:29.298 --> 07:30.758
who wants that?

07:31.467 --> 07:36.096
I'm saving myself until marriage,
and I'll use force if necessary.

07:39.475 --> 07:42.252
What's all that about
restoring your virginity?

07:42.352 --> 07:44.338
I mean, physically, you're a virgin once.

07:44.438 --> 07:48.550
Yeah, and it's not about reversing
the violation of your blessed womb.

07:48.650 --> 07:51.320
It's about Jesus
granting you a virginal heart.

07:51.737 --> 07:53.489
That way, you're pure again.

07:54.323 --> 07:55.449
Do it.

07:57.284 --> 07:59.770
My next move was clear.

07:59.870 --> 08:01.330
Nice.

08:02.372 --> 08:03.707
You're getting the hang of it.

08:29.983 --> 08:31.693
How are you doing? What's going on?

08:45.290 --> 08:46.708
What's going on?

09:02.266 --> 09:03.959
Sure, it was a radical step,

09:04.059 --> 09:07.629
but why else had Jesus
directed me to the gun range?

09:07.729 --> 09:09.565
Thank you, Jesus.

09:25.581 --> 09:29.068
Having asked Jesus to restore
my emotional and spiritual virginity

09:29.168 --> 09:31.320
in exchange for curing Dean,

09:31.420 --> 09:34.798
I started my senior year
with all of that behind me.

09:37.092 --> 09:39.636
This new van is amazing.

09:40.262 --> 09:41.555
Thanks.

09:44.099 --> 09:46.168
It's official.

09:46.268 --> 09:48.937
The Christian Jewels...
I bought one for everybody.

09:49.688 --> 09:51.607
