have noticed the beautiful billboard

15:10.426 --> 15:12.661
designed and painted
by our own Hilary Faye

15:12.761 --> 15:14.455
and donated by her father.

15:14.555 --> 15:15.848
Thank you.

15:16.932 --> 15:18.100
