24:13.936 --> 24:15.880
I'm having a vision of the Virgin Mary.

24:15.980 --> 24:17.548
Cassandra, are you all right?

24:17.648 --> 24:20.509
What she needs to do
is accept Jesus into her heart.

24:20.609 --> 24:22.386
I think what she needs is a ride home.

24:22.486 --> 24:24.180
- I'll take her.
- I'll help you, then.

24:24.280 --> 24:25.514
Come on, Cassandra.

24:25.614 --> 24:27.741
No, no, let go of the pizza.

24:28.701 --> 24:30.119
Get off of me!

24:31.287 --> 24:33.689
Helping Patrick
haul Cassandra out of the mall

24:33.789 --> 24:36.525
was like the most perfect
God-centered moment.

24:36.625 --> 24:39.737
You really learn a lot about a boy
when you're servicing the Lord.

24:39.837 --> 24:41.906
Hilary Faye, I can see your pad.

24:42.006 --> 24:44.700
- I can see a little bit of it right...
- Quit it!

24:44.800 --> 24:49.705
Slowly raise up through the knees,
still bent at the waist, and roll to standing.

24:49.805 --> 24:50.831
Good.

24:50.931 --> 24:52.750
And twist and hold.

24:52.850 --> 24:55.895
Come on. Keep holding.

24:56.729 --> 24:59.006
I know what you're looking at, Mary.

24:59.106 --> 25:00.608
And Jesus does, too,

25:13.996 --> 25:17.358
After a threatening letter
from the State Board of Education,

25:17.458 --> 25:20.820
they finally broke down
and created a Sex-Ed class.

25:20.920 --> 25:23.072
A little too late, I might add.

25:23.172 --> 25:25.758
So, it's all about populating the planet.

25:26.592 --> 25:29.929
And good Christians don't
get jiggy with it until they're married.

25:30.429 --> 25:31.472
Lights.

25:34.767 --> 25:35.935
Yes, Mary.

25:38.520 --> 25:44.902
Is it possible Jesus might need us
to do his will by, you know, not waiting?

25:47.696 --> 25:49.974
Of course, he wants us to wait.

25:50.074 --> 25:53.118
I don't think I get what you mean, Mary.

25:55.663 --> 25:57.106
I don't know.

25:57.206 --> 26:00.985
Which variety of bass
is not indigenous to North America?

26:01.085 --> 26:02.611
- B... small mouth.
- Peacock.

26:02.711 --> 26:06.198
- Large mouth?
- I'm sorry. That's incorrect.

26:06.298 --> 26:08.242
This religious figure was best known

26:08.342 --> 26:11.579
for offering to God
a sacrifice of one of his sons.

26:11.679 --> 26:13.372
- Moses!
- Brenda.

26:13.472 --> 26:15.833
I... I'm guessing Abraham?

26:15.933 --> 26:17.960
- That's correct.
- Oh, really?

26:18.060 --> 26:21.255
- Congratulations. Well done.
- I hate this show.

26:21.355 --> 26:23.466
Coming up on Lifetime,

26:23.566 --> 26:26.969
Valerie Bertinelli
stars in "Bitter Harvest"...

26:27.069 --> 26:30.055
a sensitive portrayal
of one woman's struggle with cancer.

26:30.155 --> 26:31.740
This looks good.

26:33.075 --> 26:35.494
There was a feeling
of twilight in the air...

26:36.912 --> 26:39.482
all honeydew and lilac.

26:39.582 --> 26:41.792
God wasn't just smiling down on me...

26:42.877 --> 26:45.379
he was jumping up and cheering.

26:46.505 --> 26:47.798
And then, well...

26:49.341 --> 26:50.826
I thought I was pregnant.

26:50.926 --> 26:52.620
I'd been throwing up every morning

26:52.720 --> 26:55.164
and hadn't had my period in two months.

26:55.264 --> 26:57.625
So I took a home pregnancy test.

26:57.725 --> 26:59.101
What happened?

27:02.646 --> 27:04.398
I found out I wasn't pregnant.

27:06.317 --> 27:07.860
It was the cancer.

27:09.737 --> 27:12.907
She found all that out
from a home pregnancy test?

27:13.908 --> 27:18.020
Valerie's struggles made me realize
that my problems weren't so bad.

27:18.120 --> 27:21.565
Dean was getting help,
and I still had the Jewels.

27:21.665 --> 27:23.417
I was gonna be okay.

27:41.477 --> 27:44.380
- You work here, too?
- Yeah, I'm saving up for a car.

27:44.480 --> 27:47.107
When I get one I can
come pick you up and stuff.

27:48.359 --> 27:49.527
You okay?

27:50.027 --> 27:52.154
Yeah, it's just really hot in here.

27:52.988 --> 27:54.615
- I'll see you later.
- Promise?

28:00.955 --> 28:03.832
Please let it be cancer.
Please let it be cancer.

28:37.199 --> 28:41.036
The test mentions something
about a possible false positive.

28:46.584 --> 28:48.752
Do you have anything later on Monday?

28:52.715 --> 28:56.452
3:00? No, no, I can make that.

28:56.552 --> 29:00.431
I have my leadership meeting
tonight after work.

29:03.225 --> 29:05.753
- You're not wearing that, are you?
- Why not?

29:05.853 --> 29:07.396
You just can't, Mom.

29:09.064 --> 29:11.108
You're right, it's too hot for a sweater.

29:14.278 --> 29:16.614
- I'll see you later.
- Bye, hon.

29:20.242 --> 29:23.687
Hey, Mary.
Sorry to hear about Dean's faggotry.

29:23.787 --> 29:26.373
- What?
- See you at P, circle?

29:36.217 --> 29:37.468
Can I talk to you?

29:41.096 --> 29:42.973
What's going on?

29:43.849 --> 29:45.392
You promised me.

29:49.939 --> 29:51.298
It's hard.

29:51.398 --> 29:54.735
But I think this is the only way
we can actually help Dean.

29:56.195 --> 29:58.013
Don't you think?

29:58.113 --> 30:01.058
Come on. You're not born a gay.

30:01.158 --> 30:02.701
You're born-again.

30:03.327 --> 30:05.287
I don't know what I think anymore.

30:05.955 --> 30:07.581
I've gotta go.

30:08.290 --> 30:10.025
Wait. Don't you need me
to give you a ride home?

30:10.125 --> 30:11.610
Not today, Hil.

30:11.710 --> 30:15.089
Okay. Well, tonight
at the prayer circle meeting then, okay?

30:18.133 --> 30:20.995
Prayer circle meeting at my house at 7:00.

30:21.095 --> 30:24.098
I'm conducting it
for Mary's gay boyfriend Dean.

30:38.654 --> 30:39.780
What?

30:40.948 --> 30:43.450
You know where a guy can get some smokes?

30:58.674 --> 30:59.742
What's the matter?

30:59.842 --> 31:02.161
Scared to be seen
in public with a stripper?

31:02.261 --> 31:04.747
No. Scared of being seen with a cripple?

31:04.847 --> 31:06.265
I've been seen with worse.

31:06.849 --> 31:09.418
Hilary Faye's gonna freak out
when I'm not there waiting for her.

31:09.518 --> 31:10.686
Who cares?

31:12.271 --> 31:14.690
It's just that I don't
get out much on my own.

31:16.066 --> 31:19.153
- I'm not really a stripper.
- I'm not really a Christian.

31:21.405 --> 31:24.100
So, how did you end up at American Eagle?

31:24.200 --> 31:26.185
I mean, you're Jewish, right?

31:26.285 --> 31:28.771
Well, after I got expelled
from my last school,

31:28.871 --> 31:31.165
it was either here or home schooling.

31:32.291 --> 31:35.544
I figured I could handle
these freaks better than my parents.

31:36.420 --> 31:37.504
Lucky me.

31:39.006 --> 31:42.593
- Are you playing footsies with me?
- Wheelies.

31:44.803 --> 31:45.846
Hey, isn't that...

31:48.557 --> 31:50.292
What is she doing downtown?

31:50.392 --> 31:53.879
There's only one reason Christian girls
come down to the Planned Parenthood.

31:53.979 --> 31:56.966
- She's planting a pipe bomb?
- Okay, two reasons.

31:57.066 --> 31:58.509
With Dean?

31:58.609 --> 32:01.153
I think there's a better chance
of that pipe bomb.

32:04.907 --> 32:07.743
I... I should get home.

32:11.247 --> 32:12.748
Yeah, you should.

33:21.150 --> 33:22.276
Shit.

33:30.784 --> 33:31.827
Fuck.

33:43.797 --> 33:45.299
Goddamn.

33:48.969 --> 33:53.207
And we pray for all the perverts, Lord,
but especially for Dean,

33:53.307 --> 33:56.335
whom at this time,
just hasn't found the right girl.

33:56.435 --> 34:01.757
We join together and beg you
to rid him of his unnatural perversions.

34:01.857 --> 34:04.301
May you lead him
out of the darkness, Lord,

34:04.401 --> 34:06.929
and into your divine light.

34:07.029 --> 34:08.364
Amen.

34:09.364 --> 34:11.934
That was good. That felt really nice.

34:12.034 --> 34:14.770
Thank you so much for that good prayer.

34:14.870 --> 34:16.897
- Hi, Mary.
- Hi.

34:16.996 --> 34:20.109
How are you? So good to see you.
We've been waiting for you.

34:20.208 --> 34:23.696
We were just finishing up, so if you
have anything else you wanna add.

34:23.795 --> 34:25.614
Jesus is still listening.

34:25.714 --> 34:27.949
Jesus isn't listening, Hilary Faye.

34:28.050 --> 34:31.911
I did everything I could to save Dean,
and he still ended up at Mercy House.

34:32.012 --> 34:32.955
Let's take a breath...

34:33.054 --> 34:35.666
What can they say and do
that I haven't already done!

34:35.766 --> 34:36.792
Don't embarrass me!

34:36.891 --> 34:39.043
We have to pray about this. Prayer works!

34:39.143 --> 34:43.007
- It's been medically proven.
- Just lay off of me, Hilary!

34:43.107 --> 34:44.190
Wait a second.

34:45.734 --> 34:47.069
Give me that.

34:48.070 --> 34:50.906
You could pollute the Jewels
and everything we stand for.

34:52.116 --> 34:54.702
And I can't have that. Good-bye.

34:56.036 --> 34:58.455
I hope you know
that this is all a waste of time.

35:07.298 --> 35:09.633
I just got off the phone with Hilary Faye.

35:10.593 --> 35:13.095
Wow! Can she be an uppity whootie-who.

35:17.725 --> 35:19.101
What's the matter?

35:19.685 --> 35:20.728
Nothing.

35:21.937 --> 35:23.272
Come on.

35:28.819 --> 35:33.182
Why do you think Dean's parents
sent him away so fast?

35:33.282 --> 35:35.976
They probably thought
they couldn't handle it by themselves.

35:36.076 --> 35:39.688
Having a child is like owning a car...

35:39.788 --> 35:42.650
I can change the oil, fill the gas tank,

35:42.750 --> 35:45.361
take it to a carwash,
but if the carburetor broke.

35:45.461 --> 35:47.822
I wouldn't have a clue
as to how to fix it.

35:47.922 --> 35:51.408
What are you saying... you'd actually
send me to a place like Mercy House?

35:51.508 --> 35:54.053
Mary, please don't tell me
you're a lesbian.

35:59.642 --> 36:01.268
Should I be worried about you?

36:02.645 --> 36:05.397
I don't need to worry about you... do I?

36:07.983 --> 36:09.151
No.

36:13.948 --> 36:16.392
My mom just compared me to a car,

36:16.492 --> 36:19.061
so me having a baby

36:19.161 --> 36:22.731
definitely falls into the category
of things she couldn't handle.

36:22.831 --> 36:27.653
A week after prom
and two days after I turned eighteen,

36:27.753 --> 36:30.531
I was going to join
the unwed mothers club.

36:30.631 --> 36:34.385
Dean, I'm really sorry about what we did.

36:35.344 --> 36:37.621
I mean, we should've
at least used protection.

36:37.721 --> 36:39.498
But you're the only person I've been with.

36:39.598 --> 36:42.126
- No, I know that.
- I don't have anything.

36:42.226 --> 36:44.295
It's just... Dean, I really...

36:44.395 --> 36:46.589
I need to tell you something.

36:46.689 --> 36:49.650
- Hey, governor.
- Hi, Mitch.

36:51.694 --> 36:54.096
- Mitch?
- He's my roommate.

36:54.196 --> 36:56.390
He's here for the same reason as me.

36:56.490 --> 36:58.100
He even ran away from home
to San Francisco.

36:58.200 --> 37:00.478
He's like the worst one here.

37:00.578 --> 37:03.397
- You better be careful.
- I'm gonna beat this.

37:03.497 --> 37:05.708
According to the brochure,
hundreds of others have.

37:06.375 --> 37:07.751
What were you gonna say?

37:11.005 --> 37:12.715
Nothing. Just...

37:14.550 --> 37:16.994
I wanted to know if you'd be out by prom.

37:17.094 --> 37:19.663
- Wild horses couldn't stop me.
- Mercy House residents...

37:19.763 --> 37:21.999
I gotta go. We're doing
a Christian haunted house.

37:22.099 --> 37:23.267
Happy Halloween.

37:27.813 --> 37:31.066
Let's go, let's go. Let's pick it up.

37:35.029 --> 37:36.639
Nice costume.

37:36.739 --> 37:37.990
Thanks.

37:40.034 --> 37:42.036
'Cause we have the same...

37:46.832 --> 37:49.819
If you don't let go, I'll tell everybody
you touch me inappropriately

37:49.919 --> 37:51.654
while helping me in the bathroom.

37:51.754 --> 37:54.657
- Is that supposed to embarrass me?
- I'm tired of you pushing me around.

37:54.757 --> 37:57.743
Well, maybe I'm tired
of pushing you around.

37:57.843 --> 37:59.620
He's all yours!

37:59.720 --> 38:01.831
Thanks. Call me later, okay?

38:01.931 --> 38:04.208
He doesn't appreciate
one thing you do for him.

38:04.308 --> 38:07.211
Without the strength and love
that Jesus provides me,

38:07.311 --> 38:09.797
do you really think Cassandra's
gonna be able to take care of him?

38:09.897 --> 38:11.132
No way.

38:11.232 --> 38:13.008
She's just gonna end up hurting him.

38:13.108 --> 38:16.011
By the look of the bruises
on his neck, she already has.

38:16.111 --> 38:17.446
Tia, please.

38:17.571 --> 38:19.448
What are you supposed to be?

38:20.449 --> 38:21.534
A roller skate.

38:22.785 --> 38:24.645
I've got something to show you.

38:24.745 --> 38:25.913
You do?

38:34.171 --> 38:36.949
You didn't just do this
for the parking permit, did you?

38:37.049 --> 38:38.217
Pretty much.

38:39.802 --> 38:42.830
In the meantime,
I was trying to find a new religion

38:42.930 --> 38:45.207
or a new God or whatever,

38:45.307 --> 38:49.086
but to tell you the truth,
they were all kind of freaking me out.

38:49.186 --> 38:54.650
I mean, sure, they can't all be right,
but they can't all be wrong, right?

39:04.201 --> 39:06.520
You know, the whole
crystal thing is so felt up.

39:06.620 --> 39:09.064
Don't you have a church
to desecrate or something?

39:09.164 --> 39:11.166
Roland and I saw you
sneaking out of the clinic.

39:11.917 --> 39:14.336
Kudos on the Bono shades, by the way.

39:15.004 --> 39:17.281
I was distributing pamphlets.

39:17.381 --> 39:20.593
I was trying to prevent
girls like you from making a mistake.

39:21.886 --> 39:22.970
Thank you.

39:24.013 --> 39:25.956
After we win the costume contest,

39:26.056 --> 39:29.085
we'll distribute religious tracts
to the kids instead of candy.

39:29.185 --> 39:31.921
- Good one.
- That's awesome.

39:32.021 --> 39:33.063
Hey, ladies.

39:33.772 --> 39:36.425
- Sorry. You got a second?
- Yeah.

39:36.525 --> 39:38.819
Listen, I'm concerned about Mary.

39:39.153 --> 39:40.387
Something's going on.

39:40.487 --> 39:41.889
Yeah, me too.

39:41.989 --> 39:46.160
Well, she's part of your posse,
and I think that you could help her.

39:47.119 --> 39:50.147
I'm gonna need you to be a warrior
out on the front lines for Jesus.

39:50.247 --> 39:51.874
You mean like shoot her?

39:54.168 --> 39:57.780
No, no, I was thinking
of something a little less gangsta.

39:57.880 --> 40:01.826
I need someone who's spiritually armed
to help guide her back to her faith,

40:01.926 --> 40:04.495
to love and care
that only Jesus can supply.

40:04.595 --> 40:06.664
- You down with that?
- Yeah, I'm down with that.

40:06.764 --> 40:10.351
She's pretty vulnerable right now,
so I'm gonna need you to be extra gentle.

40:11.393 --> 40:14.380
- Hurry! Hurry! Come on!
- I'm going! I'm going!

40:14.480 --> 40:15.898
- Get her!
- Come on, Tia!

40:17.775 --> 40:19.568
Stuff her in here! Hurry up! Hurry Up!

40:24.073 --> 40:25.683
In the name of Jesus Christ.

40:25.783 --> 40:27.810
I command you,
leave the body of this servant of God.

40:27.910 --> 40:30.563
You're performing
an exorcism on me? Get off me!

40:30.663 --> 40:32.481
Where are you going? Get back here!

40:32.581 --> 40:34.358
We've gotta get rid of the evil in you.

40:34.458 --> 40:36.235
- It's God's will!
- God's will?

40:36.335 --> 40:39.488
- Christ died for your sins!
- Okay, wait a second.

40:39.588 --> 40:41.699
Are you not gonna accept our intervention?

40:41.799 --> 40:43.033
You mean kidnapping? No!

40:43.133 --> 40:45.327
You are backsliding
into the flames of hell.

40:45.427 --> 40:48.456
You've become a magnet for sin.
We've all witnessed it.

40:48.556 --> 40:50.875
Sure. Veronica acting all pure.

40:50.975 --> 40:53.544
What about last spring break
at the Promise Maker's rally?

40:53.644 --> 40:57.465
You are making accusations
as we're trying to save your soul?

40:57.565 --> 40:59.925
Mary, turn away from Satan.

41:00.025 --> 41:02.678
Jesus... he loves you.

41:02.778 --> 41:06.240
You don't know the first thing about love.

41:06.949 --> 41:09.410
I am filled with Christ's love!

41:10.327 --> 41:12.855
You are just jealous
of my success in the Lord.

41:12.955 --> 41:16.876
This is not a weapon, you idiot.

41:27.303 --> 41:30.431
What, did they send you to
strap me on the back of your scooter?

41:31.098 --> 41:33.851
Scooter? Mary, this is a Vespa.

41:34.852 --> 41:37.021
And I don't know
what you're talking about. Hop on.

41:38.731 --> 41:40.508
I'd rather walk.

41:40.608 --> 41:42.109
Suit yourself.

41:47.656 --> 41:49.767
She actually tried to exorcise you?

41:49.867 --> 41:50.868
Yeah.

41:51.619 --> 41:53.120
That was nice of her, I guess.

41:54.496 --> 41:57.333
The way things have been going.
I probably should've let her.

41:58.959 --> 42:00.127
Listen, Mary...

42:01.962 --> 42:04.573
I want you to know that I don't think
Dean's sick or anything.

42:04.673 --> 42:07.201
- Yeah, right.
- No, really.

42:07.301 --> 42:10.579
Mercy House doesn't really exist
for the people who get sent there.

42:10.679 --> 42:13.249
It exists more for the people
who do the sending.

42:13.349 --> 42:16.685
So why were you at Hilary Faye's
when she was praying for Dean?

42:19.104 --> 42:20.147
Honestly...

42:22.191 --> 42:24.026
I thought you'd be there.

42:31.992 --> 42:34.854
Well, thank you for the ride, Patrick.

42:34.954 --> 42:36.288
Any time.

42:42.920 --> 42:44.672
Do you wanna go out sometime?

42:46.882 --> 42:49.326
What... are you gonna
take me out on your scooter?

42:49.426 --> 42:52.997
Come on. I'm, like, totally adorable.

42:53.097 --> 42:55.766
Besides, it would drive Hilary Faye crazy.

42:59.645 --> 43:02.898
I can't. I'm not dating right now.

43:04.066 --> 43:06.527
What about tomorrow night?
Will you be dating then?

43:09.238 --> 43:10.948
Good night, Patrick.

43:12.366 --> 43:14.034
Thank you so much.

43:14.368 --> 43:16.871
You guys are so sweet. You know what?

43:18.330 --> 43:19.373
We need to...

43:22.293 --> 43:23.444
We need to take a moment

43:23.544 --> 43:25.654
and think about those people
who aren't as fortunate

43:25.754 --> 43:27.740
to have the body of Christ
in their life right now.

43:27.840 --> 43:31.494
So, let's... let's pray for Mary.

43:31.594 --> 43:33.579
Lucky for me, at our school,

43:33.679 --> 43:37.792
teen pregnancy was about as common
as the flesh-eating virus.

43:37.892 --> 43:39.543
No one really seemed to catch on.

43:39.643 --> 43:40.711
All right, students...

43:40.811 --> 43:42.588
Except Cassandra.

43:42.688 --> 43:45.674
...and we're going to continue
with the Beatitudes.

43:45.774 --> 43:47.843
- Let's... Mary?
- Could I have a bathroom pass?

43:47.943 --> 43:49.220
- Sure.
- Thanks.

43:49.320 --> 43:52.014
Blessed are those who are persecuted
because of righteousness,

43:52.114 --> 43:54.350
for theirs is the kingdom of Heaven.

43:54.450 --> 43:57.228
Blessed are you when people
insult you, persecute you,

43:57.328 --> 44:00.414
and falsely say all kinds of evil
against you because of me.

44:06.879 --> 44:07.922
Excuse me.

44:10.466 --> 44:13.202
It doesn't bother you to have
people smoking around you?

44:13.302 --> 44:14.803
It's so bad for the baby.

44:15.971 --> 44:18.599
I'm not pregnant, okay?

44:19.308 --> 44:22.895
So, what's your plan?
It's too late for the big A.

44:23.896 --> 44:27.383
You look like a smuggler.
I know somewhere you could sell it.

44:27.483 --> 44:28.984
I'm not gonna sell my...

44:36.784 --> 44:38.285
It's Dean's, isn't it?

44:40.579 --> 44:43.249
You can't do this on your own.

44:44.750 --> 44:46.001
Yes, I can.

44:47.545 --> 44:49.505
No, you can't.

44:57.972 --> 44:59.682
I thought I was helping him.

45:02.351 --> 45:03.686
I thought it was...

45:04.603 --> 45:06.564
what Jesus wanted me to do.

45:10.067 --> 45:11.902
That's pretty stupid, right?

45:13.404 --> 45:15.389
